Craig et all,
I just posted some pics a few minutes ago on my case nut research this
morning. To boil it all down into a couple of sentences, I found that if you
dump the massively thick washers that come with the case and use some factory
washers, you can probably achieve the desired results. check my pics.

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3
71 Trike 1776cc Dual T-4 34 PDSIT-3
VolksAir 1585cc 31 PICT
